WEBVTT

00:01.135 --> 00:05.136
♪♪

00:05.205 --> 00:06.604
Hey, Apple Bloom!

00:06.673 --> 00:10.141
Rarity's re-organizing her
shop and look what she found!

00:10.210 --> 00:12.277
Old costumes from
the talent show!

00:14.615 --> 00:16.181
We thought they'd come in handy

00:16.250 --> 00:18.183
in case we ever help
a pony put on a play

00:18.252 --> 00:20.719
or need to make a quick
escape disguised as clowns!

00:24.691 --> 00:26.658
Here you go, Big Mac.

00:26.727 --> 00:30.328
Whoa! That sure is
a lot of apples!

00:30.397 --> 00:32.864
Are you making another delivery
to Starlight's old village?

00:32.933 --> 00:34.199
Yeeeup.

00:34.268 --> 00:37.202
That's an awful long way
for a pony to go, isn't it?

00:37.271 --> 00:38.303
Yeeeup.

00:38.372 --> 00:39.505
You've been going
there a lot lately.

00:39.573 --> 00:42.574
What is this? Your
fifth trip this week?

00:42.643 --> 00:44.442
[giggle]

00:44.511 --> 00:45.510
Yeeeup.

00:45.579 --> 00:47.512
OK, well, have fun!

00:47.581 --> 00:50.181
So what other costumes did
you bring, Sweetie Belle?

00:50.250 --> 00:51.516
Are you crazy?

00:51.585 --> 00:54.752
We can't talk about costumes
at a time like this!

00:54.821 --> 00:56.454
Time like what?

00:56.523 --> 00:58.890
Your brother is
hiding something.

00:58.959 --> 01:01.526
Did you see the
way he was acting?

01:01.595 --> 01:04.129
Yeah, he totally blushed
when you brought up

01:04.198 --> 01:06.731
how often he's been going
to Starlight's old village.

01:06.800 --> 01:09.434
Something is
definitely going on.

01:09.503 --> 01:11.336
There can only be one reason

01:11.405 --> 01:14.906
a pony would travel
so far, so often.

01:14.975 --> 01:16.407
He's taking private
skiing lessons!

01:16.476 --> 01:17.542
He's training for a marathon!

01:17.610 --> 01:18.743
I've been cooking
a lot of broccoli

01:18.812 --> 01:20.612
and he wants to get
away from the smell!

01:20.681 --> 01:23.148
[laughter]

01:25.419 --> 01:28.720
<i>♪ My little pony,</i>
<i>my little pony ♪</i>

01:28.789 --> 01:30.688
<i>♪ Aaaahhh ♪</i>

01:30.757 --> 01:32.357
<i>♪ My little Pony ♪</i>

01:32.425 --> 01:35.293
<i>♪ I used to wonder what</i>
<i>friendship could be. ♪</i>

01:35.362 --> 01:37.062
<i>♪ My Little Pony ♪</i>

01:37.130 --> 01:39.631
<i>♪ Until you all shared</i>
<i>its magic with me. ♪</i>

01:39.700 --> 01:41.433
<i>♪ Big adventure! ♪</i>
<i>♪ Tons of fun ♪</i>

01:41.502 --> 01:43.268
<i>♪ A beautiful heart! ♪ ♪</i>
<i>Faithful and strong! ♪</i>

01:43.337 --> 01:45.771
<i>♪ Sharing kindness ♪</i>
<i>♪ it's an easy feat ♪</i>

01:45.840 --> 01:48.173
<i>♪ And magic makes it</i>
<i>all complete! ♪</i>

01:48.242 --> 01:50.308
<i>♪ To have my little pony ♪</i>

01:50.377 --> 01:53.611
<i>♪ Do you know you're all</i>
<i>my very best friends? ♪</i>

01:53.680 --> 01:56.482
♪♪

02:00.754 --> 02:04.856
♪♪

02:04.925 --> 02:09.227
Maybe he's a spy on a mission
to thwart an evil villain

02:09.296 --> 02:10.728
with his secret weapon:

02:10.797 --> 02:12.830
an apple cannon!

02:12.899 --> 02:16.668
No, that's crazy. I think
it's my broccoli thing.

02:16.737 --> 02:18.570
Why don't we just
ask him?

02:18.639 --> 02:21.406
You saw how shifty he
was acting earlier.

02:21.475 --> 02:23.708
There's no way he'll
tell us what he's doing.

02:23.777 --> 02:26.377
Plus, I really want
to go undercover.

02:26.446 --> 02:28.313
We already
have costumes.

02:28.382 --> 02:31.950
Call me: Agent Rainbowhead.

02:32.019 --> 02:35.486
I'll be Shimmering Spectacles:

02:35.555 --> 02:39.424
a librarian with
a mysterious past.

02:39.493 --> 02:42.794
And I'll be a pirate
spy. Argh. A spyrate!

02:48.435 --> 02:50.835
Avast! Our ship be leaving port!

02:50.904 --> 02:51.469
Huh?

02:51.538 --> 02:53.305
Big Mac's leaving.

02:54.641 --> 02:57.276
If we're gonna be
spies, we gotta go NOW!

03:06.453 --> 03:08.286
[whistling]

03:08.355 --> 03:10.755
Big Mac's comin'!
Quick, act like apples!

03:10.824 --> 03:12.257
What? How?

03:17.397 --> 03:25.603
♪♪

03:25.672 --> 03:28.473
[no audio]

03:28.542 --> 03:29.907
Who's that pony?

03:29.976 --> 03:31.210
Let me see!

03:35.582 --> 03:37.982
I don't know. Shouldn't
have taken the binoculars.

03:38.051 --> 03:40.285
I don't know
anypony here.

03:40.354 --> 03:41.853
That must be
Sugar Belle.

03:41.922 --> 03:43.921
Applejack told me
about her bakery.

03:43.990 --> 03:46.358
Obviously, she's just been
ordering a lot of apples.

03:51.698 --> 03:53.498
So nothing fishy's
going on.

03:53.567 --> 03:56.668
No way! We came
here to be spies!

03:56.737 --> 04:00.038
And no spy I know has ever
solved a case that quick.

04:00.107 --> 04:02.440
How many spies
do you know?

04:02.509 --> 04:04.309
That's not important.

04:04.378 --> 04:08.513
What's important is
that we do more recon!

04:08.582 --> 04:09.614
Follow my lead.

04:09.683 --> 04:19.791
♪♪

04:19.860 --> 04:23.027
Whoa, she sure likes her apples!

04:23.096 --> 04:27.365
What is she doing? Making the
biggest apple pie in Equestria?

04:27.434 --> 04:29.735
Thanks for coming all
this way, Big Mac.

04:32.839 --> 04:35.840
It sure is nice seeing
you again so soon.

04:35.909 --> 04:38.710
♪♪

04:38.779 --> 04:41.679
Yeeeup.

04:41.748 --> 04:44.482
All I used to bake were
boring old muffins.

04:44.551 --> 04:46.351
But thanks to your
apple deliveries,

04:46.420 --> 04:48.820
I get to bake all kinds
of delicious treats!

04:48.889 --> 04:51.856
... apple pies, apple
fritters, apple turnovers,

04:51.925 --> 04:54.692
caramel apples,
caramel apple cakes...

04:54.761 --> 04:55.994
[sigh]

04:56.062 --> 04:59.097
I just wish I had more
room to display it all.

04:59.166 --> 05:02.467
My shelves only hold so much.

05:02.536 --> 05:06.571
I'm telling you, this pony
really likes her apples!

05:06.640 --> 05:08.873
[gasp] Or Big Mac!

05:08.942 --> 05:09.907
Huh?

05:09.976 --> 05:11.642
Just look!

05:11.711 --> 05:12.977
Ooh! Uh!

05:13.046 --> 05:16.581
[giggle]

05:16.650 --> 05:19.384
Sweetie Belle, I
think you're right!

05:19.453 --> 05:21.386
I think my brother has a crush!

05:21.455 --> 05:22.387
Shhhh!

05:27.461 --> 05:28.727
Psst! Big Mac!

05:31.865 --> 05:34.665
Now remember, my
brother's super shy

05:34.734 --> 05:37.735
so he's probably going to be
embarrassed about his crush.

05:37.804 --> 05:39.438
Just try and make
him feel comfortable.

05:40.974 --> 05:44.175
Hey, Big Mac! It's
me: Apple Bloom!

05:44.244 --> 05:45.543
Yeeeup.

05:45.612 --> 05:47.145
We're here, too!

05:47.214 --> 05:48.913
Mm hm.

05:48.982 --> 05:52.617
I'm going to ask you a
very personal question

05:52.686 --> 05:54.820
and I want you to
answer honestly.

05:57.057 --> 06:01.526
Do you... have a crush...
on... Sugar Belle?

06:01.595 --> 06:03.461
Yeeeup.

06:03.530 --> 06:04.729
Well, that was easy!

06:04.798 --> 06:06.164
This is so exciting!

06:06.233 --> 06:09.033
My big brother has
his very first crush!

06:09.102 --> 06:12.136
First crush? What
about Cheerilee?

06:12.205 --> 06:14.005
It doesn't really count
when you trick a pony

06:14.074 --> 06:16.541
into drinking a love
potion, does it?

06:16.610 --> 06:18.209
Nope.

06:18.278 --> 06:21.612
My brother has a cra-ush!
My brother has a cra-ush!

06:21.681 --> 06:23.815
My brother has a cra-ush!

06:23.884 --> 06:26.184
Wait. Does Sugar Belle
even know you like her?

06:26.253 --> 06:27.885
Nuh uh.

06:27.954 --> 06:29.687
Then you gotta
tell her!

06:29.756 --> 06:32.490
[gulp]

06:32.559 --> 06:34.525
We're pretty sure
she likes you!

06:34.594 --> 06:36.127
I mean, she keeps
ordering apples

06:36.196 --> 06:37.862
just so she can
see you again!

06:37.931 --> 06:39.764
Ya think so?

06:39.833 --> 06:43.901
Totally. But you'll never
know if you don't try.

06:43.970 --> 06:45.003
OK.

06:47.240 --> 06:49.073
Go get 'er, Big Mac!

06:49.142 --> 07:00.751
♪♪

07:00.820 --> 07:02.854
[crash]

07:02.923 --> 07:06.190
Hey girl. I was writing
poetry by the pond

07:06.259 --> 07:08.092
when I saw these flowers.

07:08.161 --> 07:10.628
I thought I'd show them
how pretty you are.

07:10.697 --> 07:12.964
Oh. Thanks,
Feather Bangs!

07:19.039 --> 07:22.607
Um, is it possible to
have two crushes at once?

07:22.676 --> 07:26.077
Because it looks like Big
Mac may not be the only pony

07:26.146 --> 07:27.746
Sugar Belle likes!

07:31.952 --> 07:34.652
♪♪

07:34.721 --> 07:37.288
Hey, Big Mac! Where you goin'?

07:37.357 --> 07:38.590
Home.

07:38.658 --> 07:40.525
You can't let that Feather
fella get in the way

07:40.594 --> 07:42.059
of your one true love.

07:42.128 --> 07:43.794
You've gotta take him down!

07:43.863 --> 07:45.696
What can he do that you can't?

07:45.765 --> 07:46.897
That!

07:46.966 --> 07:49.800
Whoops! Ha ha. These
balls are like you.

07:49.869 --> 07:52.036
I'll always catch
you if you fall.

07:52.105 --> 07:53.672
[swooning]

07:55.241 --> 07:57.808
Seriously? That line worked?

07:57.877 --> 07:59.810
She'll never pick me.

07:59.879 --> 08:02.680
Sure she will, cause
we're gonna help you!

08:02.749 --> 08:04.882
No love potions!

08:04.951 --> 08:07.818
[laughter]

08:07.887 --> 08:11.856
Don't worry, Big Mac. We learned
our lesson the hard way.

08:11.925 --> 08:14.625
Yeah, we're never
gonna do that again.

08:14.694 --> 08:16.794
Besides, I know
exactly what to do!

08:16.863 --> 08:19.864
When I was younger I
read all the fairy tales.

08:19.933 --> 08:21.832
When you were
younger, huh?

08:21.901 --> 08:25.670
Well, I was younger
on the way here.

08:25.739 --> 08:27.905
It was a long ride!

08:27.974 --> 08:30.308
Anyway, as long as we
do what the book says,

08:30.377 --> 08:32.277
you're pretty much
guaranteed a happy ending!

08:35.081 --> 08:36.280
How 'bout this one?!

08:36.349 --> 08:40.918
Rescuing a damsel pony in
distress. That's perfect.

08:40.987 --> 08:43.988
Of course, we'll have to
improvise without a dragon.

08:44.057 --> 08:47.024
Too bad Spike isn't here. Not
that he's very threatening.

08:47.093 --> 08:49.293
[giggles]

08:49.362 --> 08:51.228
So what should we do?

08:51.297 --> 08:53.030
Wait around for Sugar
Belle to get herself

08:53.099 --> 08:55.266
into a scary situation?

08:55.335 --> 08:58.369
OR we bring the danger to her!

08:58.438 --> 08:59.871
[gulp]

09:04.377 --> 09:06.911
All right, Scootaloo's
gonna pretend to take

09:06.980 --> 09:10.615
Sugar Belle's things, then you
swoop in and stop her. Ready?

09:12.318 --> 09:14.285
Nope.

09:14.354 --> 09:17.154
C'mon, you're gonna be her hero!

09:17.223 --> 09:19.624
In fairy tales, the
Knight in Shining Armor

09:19.693 --> 09:21.092
always gets the girl.

09:32.806 --> 09:34.905
Somepony help!

09:34.974 --> 09:40.011
♪♪

09:48.221 --> 09:53.258
Here's your sugar, Sugar. Though
it is not as sweet as you.

09:55.729 --> 09:58.262
[swooning]

09:58.331 --> 09:59.898
Thank you, Feather!

10:01.901 --> 10:04.669
That smooth-talking
pony stole our rescue!

10:04.738 --> 10:06.203
And it totally
would have worked!

10:06.272 --> 10:07.705
Eeyup!

10:07.774 --> 10:09.674
We're just gonna
have to keep trying!

10:09.743 --> 10:12.276
Big Mac, are you ready
to take it up a notch?

10:12.345 --> 10:13.845
Oh, Eeyup!

10:15.949 --> 10:17.882
Oh, Nope.

10:17.951 --> 10:21.185
Trust us. There's nothing
more romantic than waking

10:21.254 --> 10:23.087
your special pony
from a sleeping spell

10:23.156 --> 10:25.189
with a magical kiss!

10:25.258 --> 10:28.726
See? They rode off
into the sunset.

10:28.795 --> 10:30.828
[sighs]

10:30.897 --> 10:32.197
Any sign of Feather Bangs?

10:37.203 --> 10:39.870
Negative. Coast is clear!

10:39.939 --> 10:42.073
It's now or never, Big Mac!

10:42.142 --> 10:43.274
[gulp]

10:57.390 --> 11:00.357
[smooch]

11:00.426 --> 11:02.927
Ah!

11:02.996 --> 11:07.064
Oh, girl, you've been
workin' hard all day.

11:07.133 --> 11:10.802
Allow me to treat you
like the princess you are!

11:13.473 --> 11:16.040
[sighs]

11:16.109 --> 11:20.444
Hey! That's our metaphorical
sunset they're riding off into!

11:20.513 --> 11:23.314
All right. This ends now!

11:23.383 --> 11:25.816
Feather Bangs may
have good timing.

11:25.885 --> 11:30.221
And a good mane. But let's
see him compete with a song!

11:30.290 --> 11:32.089
Say what now?!

11:32.158 --> 11:35.192
Of course! Why didn't
we think of it before?

11:35.261 --> 11:39.163
Every great love story hinges
on the romantic musical number!

11:39.232 --> 11:42.399
Big Mac, you've gotta write
a song for Sugar Belle!

11:42.468 --> 11:43.902
Eyup!

11:46.940 --> 11:51.008
♪♪

11:51.077 --> 11:52.843
Come on, Big Mac!

11:52.912 --> 11:56.514
Feather Bangs is
so romantic

11:56.583 --> 12:00.051
When he speaks, I pretend
he's talking to me.

12:01.554 --> 12:05.523
Come on! You can do better than
him! Just like we practiced.

12:05.592 --> 12:06.925
[gulp]

12:14.901 --> 12:17.001
<i>♪ [country guitar] ♪</i>

12:17.070 --> 12:20.038
<i>♪ We'll take a walk</i>
<i>down by the river. ♪</i>

12:22.942 --> 12:26.111
<i>♪ Watch the sunset</i>
<i>from the field. ♪</i>

12:28.948 --> 12:34.218
<i>♪ We'll plant the seeds</i>
<i>of love together. ♪</i>

12:34.287 --> 12:39.557
<i>♪ And water them right</i>
<i>for a really good yield. ♪</i>

12:39.626 --> 12:46.096
<i>♪ Sugar Belle sweet as pie.</i>
<i>You're the apple of my eye. ♪</i>

12:46.165 --> 12:51.268
<i>♪ A cherry blossom</i>
<i>in a field of rye. ♪</i>

12:51.337 --> 12:55.039
<i>♪ And when the heifer's</i>
<i>milked and fed ♪</i>

12:55.108 --> 12:58.075
<i>♪ and the pigs are</i>
<i>in the sty, ♪</i>

12:58.144 --> 13:01.846
<i>♪ won't you be there</i>
<i>by my side?♪</i>

13:03.082 --> 13:06.217
<i>♪ Oh, oh. Oh, oh. ♪</i>

13:06.286 --> 13:10.187
<i>♪ When you appeared before me</i>
<i>my heart stopped beating. ♪</i>

13:10.256 --> 13:14.158
<i>♪ Stars crossed the sky to</i>
<i>come see what I was seeing. ♪</i>

13:14.227 --> 13:20.531
<i>♪ You were the one that made</i>
<i>me believe I could fly. ♪</i>

13:20.600 --> 13:22.300
<i>♪ Wo-ah wo-ah wo-ah. ♪</i>

13:22.368 --> 13:26.136
<i>♪ Birds could not sing a</i>
<i>song that's as beautiful ♪</i>

13:26.205 --> 13:30.107
<i>♪ I'd do anything</i>
<i>that's irrefutable ♪</i>

13:30.176 --> 13:36.213
<i>♪ cause you are the sun</i>
<i>painting my heart in the sky. ♪</i>

13:36.282 --> 13:40.150
<i>♪ Whoa-oh Sugar, Sugar Belle ♪</i>

13:40.219 --> 13:44.455
<i>♪ wha oh when will you tell</i>
<i>me that you feel the same ♪</i>

13:44.524 --> 13:48.292
<i>♪ like an angel on</i>
<i>a candy cane ♪</i>

13:48.361 --> 13:52.529
<i>♪ or the sunlight shining</i>
<i>through a drain. ♪</i>

13:52.598 --> 13:57.434
<i>♪ Sugar Belle, when I</i>
<i>look in your eyes, ♪</i>

13:57.503 --> 14:02.172
<i>♪ I see the colour blue</i>

14:02.241 --> 14:07.411
<i>♪ and it reminds me of</i>
<i>the sky above ♪</i>

14:07.480 --> 14:12.049
<i>♪ which is also blue. ♪</i>

14:12.118 --> 14:13.751
<i>♪ [dance beat] ♪</i>

14:13.820 --> 14:17.087
<i>♪ Hey, hey, hey, hey</i>
<i>Be my sugar plum. ♪</i>

14:17.156 --> 14:19.056
<i>♪ I will be your watermelon. ♪</i>

14:19.125 --> 14:22.326
<i>♪ Every time you smile, I can</i>
<i>feel my heart a swellin'. ♪</i>

14:22.395 --> 14:25.596
<i>♪ Blood is rushing from my</i>
<i>head to my hooves yeah. ♪</i>

14:25.665 --> 14:29.033
<i>♪ I start movin when I'm</i>
<i>feeling that groove, yeah. ♪</i>

14:29.102 --> 14:32.036
<i>♪ I've been writing</i>
<i>this song for you. ♪</i>

14:32.105 --> 14:35.372
<i>♪ Searching for the</i>
<i>perfect rhyme. ♪</i>

14:35.441 --> 14:39.043
<i>♪ For the words I</i>
<i>want to say... ♪</i>

14:39.112 --> 14:42.346
<i>♪ something something</i>
<i>something be mine. ♪</i>

14:42.415 --> 14:43.881
<i>♪ [dance beat] ♪</i>

14:43.950 --> 14:47.451
<i>♪ Oh, oh, oh oh.</i>
<i>Every day I see you ♪</i>

14:47.520 --> 14:50.287
<i>♪ I know you could</i>
<i>be the one for me. ♪</i>

14:50.356 --> 14:54.291
<i>♪ Feel my heart a-beating like</i>
<i>the rain upon a bumble bee ♪</i>

14:54.360 --> 14:58.062
<i>♪ don't cha see that</i>
<i>I go ah oh. Ah oh. ♪</i>

14:58.131 --> 15:02.333
<i>Whenever you are</i>
<i>near me I'm so ah oh. ♪</i>

15:02.402 --> 15:08.038
<i>♪ Sugar Belle! Roses are</i>
<i>red and violets are blue. ♪</i>

15:08.107 --> 15:12.109
<i>♪ Sugar, sugar my</i>
<i>love is burning hot ♪</i>

15:12.178 --> 15:13.510
<i>♪ like a cheese fondue! ♪</i>

15:13.579 --> 15:15.346
<i>♪ Sugar Belle! ♪</i>

15:15.415 --> 15:16.948
<i>♪ Sugar Belle! ♪</i>

15:25.691 --> 15:27.058
[crash]

15:34.233 --> 15:37.534
What in Equestria has
gotten into you two?

15:37.603 --> 15:39.269
If you think I'm
the kind of pony

15:39.338 --> 15:40.771
that likes all
this nonsense,

15:40.840 --> 15:44.008
then you clearly
don't know me at all!

15:44.077 --> 15:48.145
I wish everypony would
just LEAVE ME ALONE!

15:48.214 --> 15:51.382
<i>♪ sad music ♪</i>

15:51.451 --> 16:02.226
♪♪

16:09.102 --> 16:10.335
Big Mac!

16:13.639 --> 16:15.406
Big Mac!

16:15.475 --> 16:18.609
Well, nopony's seen him.

16:18.678 --> 16:24.114
I feel terrible. I've never seen
my brother so upset before.

16:24.183 --> 16:26.617
BIG MAC! Big Mac!

16:31.357 --> 16:32.623
Are you OK?

16:32.692 --> 16:34.825
Nope.

16:34.894 --> 16:38.128
Sorry it didn't work
out with Sugar Belle.

16:38.197 --> 16:39.663
We don't get it.

16:39.732 --> 16:43.233
Big, grand gestures always
work in the fairy tales!

16:43.302 --> 16:46.503
But Sugar Belle's not
a fairy tale princess;

16:46.572 --> 16:48.405
she's a real pony.

16:48.474 --> 16:50.741
She's kind and she works hard

16:50.810 --> 16:53.177
and she's sweeter than
everything in her bakery.

16:55.414 --> 16:58.515
That's it! We should
have been thinking about

16:58.584 --> 17:00.751
what would mean a
lot to Sugar Belle!

17:00.820 --> 17:02.519
Hmmm.

17:02.588 --> 17:04.288
[gasp]

17:04.357 --> 17:07.691
I know just the thing! But
I'm gonna need your help.

17:07.760 --> 17:10.561
Really? Even after
we messed it up?

17:10.630 --> 17:12.696
Yeeup! C'mon!

17:12.765 --> 17:23.340
♪♪

17:23.409 --> 17:27.711
Hello! My name's
Shimmering Spectacles

17:27.780 --> 17:32.583
and I'm a librarian
with a mysterious past.

17:32.652 --> 17:38.655
Oh. OK. I'm--wait a
minute. You look familiar.

17:38.724 --> 17:45.229
I shouldn't. Um... I'm new in
town. Mind showing me around?

17:45.298 --> 17:46.797
Uh, sure.

17:46.866 --> 17:50.767
That's the whole town.
It's just the one street.

17:50.836 --> 17:54.204
♪♪

17:54.273 --> 17:56.240
[clatter]

17:56.309 --> 18:01.412
Oh, no, clumsy me! Here,
let me help you clean it up.

18:03.816 --> 18:06.250
I don't think Scootaloo can
hold her off much longer!

18:08.688 --> 18:11.488
Uh... now hold on
a minute.

18:11.557 --> 18:15.292
Are you sure I
can't buy you a new bag?

18:15.361 --> 18:17.694
I'm good. It's no big deal.

18:17.763 --> 18:19.530
But... uh...

18:24.403 --> 18:28.205
OK, what's going on?

18:28.274 --> 18:31.676
The cupcake has landed! Repeat!
The cupcake has landed!

18:34.747 --> 18:35.913
Big Mac!

18:35.982 --> 18:40.584
♪♪

18:40.653 --> 18:43.420
You made me a new display case?

18:43.489 --> 18:45.355
Yeeeup...

18:45.424 --> 18:49.259
And you made it bigger!
You remembered!

18:49.328 --> 18:52.296
Now I have twice as much
room for all my desserts.

18:52.365 --> 18:56.600
[gasp] Which means...
I can make even more!

18:56.669 --> 18:59.670
I've been dying to try baking
cream pies and whoopie pies

18:59.739 --> 19:04.541
and icebox cakes and of
course, more apple treats.

19:04.610 --> 19:07.945
Oh, Big Mac, thank
you so much.

19:08.014 --> 19:11.949
This is the sweetest thing
anypony's ever done for me.

19:12.018 --> 19:18.222
Ummm... yee-- nooope... uh...

19:18.291 --> 19:20.258
I like you, too.

19:21.794 --> 19:23.827
[sigh]

19:23.896 --> 19:25.829
Awwwwwwww!

19:25.898 --> 19:28.832
That was the most
romantic thing ever!

19:28.901 --> 19:32.970
Wait a minute. I
recognize you fillies!

19:33.039 --> 19:35.839
Have they been with
you this whole time?

19:35.908 --> 19:38.408
I'm Big Mac's little sister.

19:38.477 --> 19:40.477
And these are my friends.

19:40.546 --> 19:42.479
We're sorry for everything
we put you through today,

19:42.548 --> 19:43.981
Sugar Belle.

19:44.049 --> 19:46.450
Big Mac never would have gone
through with all of those crazy

19:46.519 --> 19:47.884
Over-the-top...

19:47.953 --> 19:49.319
Downright ridiculous...

19:49.388 --> 19:52.756
attempts to impress you if
we hadn't put him up to it.

19:52.825 --> 19:55.292
But we learned our lesson!

19:55.361 --> 19:57.961
Romance isn't about
impressing somepony;

19:58.030 --> 20:00.731
it's about doing something
that means something special

20:00.800 --> 20:04.868
to that pony you lo--
[ahem] like a lot.

20:04.937 --> 20:08.338
Uh, Apple Bloom? I
think they get it.

20:08.407 --> 20:12.709
[giggle]

20:12.778 --> 20:25.489
<i>♪ Sugar Belle!! Whoa!</i>
<i>Oh! Whoa, whoa! ♪</i>

20:25.558 --> 20:29.526
Sorry, Feather. You're
a little too late.

20:29.595 --> 20:32.697
Yeah, Sugar Belle's already
picked her special somepony.

20:36.602 --> 20:37.868
But don't worry.

20:37.937 --> 20:40.738
You've got three not-so-secret
admirers right behind you!

20:42.975 --> 20:45.575
[sigh]

20:45.644 --> 20:48.312
What should I say to them?

20:48.381 --> 20:50.981
Uh. You're asking us for advice?

20:51.050 --> 20:55.052
Uh huh. Look, I can mane-flip,
write poetry and juggle,

20:55.121 --> 20:57.721
but actually talking to a pony?

20:57.790 --> 21:00.624
It scares me almost
as much as loneliness.

21:00.693 --> 21:03.593
Will you help me? Please?

21:03.662 --> 21:06.029
Gee, I don't know about this.

21:06.098 --> 21:09.499
He just needs a little nudge in
the conversation department!

21:09.568 --> 21:12.670
Besides, I don't think Big
Mac's ready to leave just yet.

21:16.642 --> 21:18.775
Let's do it!

21:18.844 --> 21:22.713
Feather Bangs, the Cutie Mark
Crusaders are at your service!

21:27.586 --> 21:30.988
[laughter]
